title: Empty Nest Season 7 (1994 - 95) fiveofseven
description:
To "The Forgotten One" on You-Tube, whoever you are...
I comprehend you are re-encoding my work for your account,
but you could at least give me credit as the source.
This project is a lot of work, that goes beyond loading a file and clicking 'start'.
There's the recording of them, sometimes twice to three times,
due to local station ID and trips in the broadcast. Editing out commercials,
using at least 2 broadcasts for each episode, so it will look nice.
Then there's the closed captions to srt conversion that is another bag of problems to get it right...
I don't mind you using my encodes, I actually like that it's out there,
but you SHOULD at least mention the source for making it possible at all!
  
https://yuq.me/users/25/564/KDbECJhTtP.jpg 
  
https://yuq.me/users/25/564/XmIEqAcxvH.png 
  

PLOT - The show revolves around pediatrician Dr. Harry Weston (Richard Mulligan), 
whose life is turned upside down when his wife, Libby, dies, and two of his three
adult daughters move back into the family home in Miami. 

Harry and Laverne are now working for a struggling inner-city medical 
clinic run by the tough-talking Dr. Maxine Douglas (Marsha Warfield). 

Carol is the only daughter living at home now and Estelle Getty reprised her 
Golden Girls character Sophia Petrillo during Empty Nest's final two seasons.
Kristy McNichol returns as Barbara for the final episode.
